      "raw_text": "A rich strike has been made in the\nHumming Bird mine at Burke in the\nOccur d'Alenes. A stringer of 10\ninches of good shipping ore has been\nencountered at a depth of about 100\nfeet, which is believed to be chute\nfrom the main level not more than\n$50 feet away."
